What I mean

336
00:31:33,660 --> 00:31:36,180
is that makes me realize

337
00:31:38,380 --> 00:31:41,220
that the only one who stands by me

338
00:31:42,220 --> 00:31:43,420
is you.

339
00:31:50,740 --> 00:31:52,260
Vee.

340
00:31:52,740 --> 00:31:54,660
I'm sorry.

341
00:31:55,620 --> 00:31:58,660
I'm sorry, Vee. I'm sorry.

342
00:32:02,220 --> 00:32:04,780
