348
00:32:48,500 --> 00:32:52,260
♪I just want to keep you smile♪

349
00:32:52,260 --> 00:32:56,180
♪I don't even want to see
a teardrop from you♪

350
00:32:56,180 --> 00:33:00,100
♪I will be there once you want me♪

351
00:33:00,100 --> 00:33:04,740
♪Being your confidant
for you to vent to♪

352
00:33:06,300 --> 00:33:10,460
♪It's alright if you love someone else♪

353
00:33:10,460 --> 00:33:14,580
♪As long as you remember
that you always have me♪

354
00:33:14,580 --> 00:33:18,620
♪It's good enough♪

355
00:33:18,620 --> 00:33:22,340
♪Because a knock-off like me
is only for replacing♪

356
00:33:22,340 --> 00:33:28,500
♪Your eyes tell me
who is the most important to you♪

357
00:33:29,540 --> 00:33:34,220
♪Even if it's not me♪

358
00:33:34,220 --> 00:33:37,860
♪The day you are no longer lonely
I might need to step back♪

